OL,3,CInside the Birmingham school
OL,4,Csupporting displaced children
OL,6,FThere are warnings that funding cuts
OL,7,Fand constant relocations are
OL,8,Fincreasing pressure on schools
OL,9,Fsupporting children who speak English
OL,10,Fas second language.
OL,12,FITV News Social Affairs Correspondent
OL,13,FSarah Corker and Senior Producer
OL,14,FLottie Kilraine report
OL,16,FDuring a Tuesday morning lesson at a
OL,17,Fsecondary school in Birmingham,
OL,18,Fchildren who have recently arrived in
OL,19,FBritain are learning basic greetings
OL,20,Fin English.
