OL,3,CInside the Birmingham school
OL,4,Csupporting displaced children
OL,6,FThe students share where they come
OL,7,Ffrom - Gaza, Yemen, Afghanistan, The
OL,8,FGambia, to name just a few. Many have
OL,9,Ffled war and persecution and speak
OL,10,Flittle or no English.
OL,12,FThe City Academy in central Birmingham
OL,13,Fruns a 12-week intensive course for
OL,14,Fthe children to learn basic English
OL,15,Fskills to help them before they start
OL,16,Fmainstream education.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/20
