OL,3,CInside the Birmingham school
OL,4,Csupporting displaced children
OL,6,FAround half of the academy's 600
OL,7,Fpupils speak English as an additional
OL,8,Flanguage, known as EAL, and 52
OL,9,Fdifferent languages are spoken within
OL,10,Fthe school.
OL,12,F"When I first came here, it felt
OL,13,Fharsh. I didn't know anything in the
OL,14,Flanguage and didn't know what people
OL,15,Fwere saying," Amrullah, aged 12, told
OL,16,FITV News.
OL,18,FHe is a year 7 pupil who started at
OL,19,FCity Academy this Autumn after his
OL,20,Ffamily fled the Taliban and arrived in
OL,21,Fthe UK on a military plane.
