OL,6,F"They helped me to read and write, and
OL,7,Fnow my English is ten times better,"
OL,8,Fhe added.
OL,10,FThe Core Hello programme, as it's
OL,11,Fknown, was set up in 2021 when the
OL,12,FCore Education Trust welcomed a number
OL,13,Fof pupils who came to the UK after the
OL,14,FTaliban takeover of Afghanistan, and
OL,15,Fthen later refugee children from
OL,16,FUkraine.
OL,18,FAmrullah is one of the 250 students
OL,19,Ffrom four academies across the city
OL,20,Fwho have benefited from this extra
OL,21,Fsupport, delivered by EAL specialists.
