OL,6,FAs well as language classes, the Core
OL,7,FHello programme focuses on
OL,8,Fintegration, including trips into the
OL,9,Fcity centre to help with cultural
OL,10,Facclimatisation, such as learning how
OL,11,Fto go food shopping or use the library.
OL,13,FAmrullah, who wants to be a doctor,
OL,14,Frecalls with joy the moment he was
OL,15,Ffirst shown a self-service checkout in
OL,16,Fa supermarket.
