OL,4,Csupporting displaced children
OL,6,FAmrullah, 12, and Fatou, 15, are two
OL,7,Fof the 250 students from four Core
OL,8,FEducation Trusts across Birmingham who
OL,9,Fhave benefited from this extra support
OL,10,Fdelivered by EAL specialists
OL,12,FAnother student taking the intensive
OL,13,FEnglish course is Fatou, who is in
OL,14,Fyear 10 and from The Gambia.
OL,16,F"I had never been in the library
OL,17,Fbefore, but they told me what to do in
OL,18,Fthere, we also went to the theatre and
OL,19,Fthe civic centre," she told ITV News.
