OL,6,FThe 15-year-old, who already speaks
OL,7,Ffive languages, came to the UK in 2024
OL,8,Fwith her father to improve her English.
OL,10,FThe number of school kids in England
OL,11,Fspeaking EAL has continued to increase
OL,12,Fover time from just under 500,000,
OL,13,F7.6% of all pupils in 1997, to 20.5%
OL,14,Fof all pupils (1.68 million) in 2023,
OL,15,Faccording to analysis from the Bell
OL,16,FFoundation.
OL,18,FLondon, the West Midlands, and the
OL,19,FNorth West have the highest number of
OL,20,Fschools with the majority of pupils
OL,21,F(over 50%) speaking EAL.
