OL,3,CInside the Birmingham school
OL,4,Csupporting displaced children
OL,6,FDiana Sutton, Director of the Bell
OL,7,FFoundation, told ITV News that some
OL,8,Fvulnerable children are 'stuck' in
OL,9,Fasylum hotels without access to
OL,10,Feducation for up to a year
OL,12,FRaj Mann, the Executive Head at the
OL,13,FCore Education Trust, told ITV News
OL,14,Fthat many of his students have at some
OL,15,Fpoint lived in Home Office hotels, and
OL,16,Flast-minute accommodation moves can
OL,17,Fdisrupt their education.
OL,19,F"We provide that stability for them,"
OL,20,Fhe said.
