OL,6,F"Some of our students and our families
OL,7,Fhave stayed in one hotel, and then
OL,8,Fthey are moved to another hotel, and
OL,9,Fthat can happen two or three times in
OL,10,Fa month. One pupil is now travelling
OL,11,Fthree hours a day on multiple buses
OL,12,Fjust to get here."
OL,14,FThe school's support doesn't just stop
OL,15,Fwith the students.
OL,17,F"We're also helping the families as
OL,18,Fwell, but it is challenging in terms
OL,19,Fof many of the families staying in
OL,20,Ftemporary accommodation," Mann added.
