OL,6,FIn the UK, all children have the legal
OL,7,Fright of access to education, with a
OL,8,Ftarget of 20 days for unaccompanied
OL,9,Fasylum-seeking children to get a
OL,10,Fschool place, but these targets are
OL,11,Fbeing missed.
OL,13,FMany displaced children are waiting
OL,14,Fover three months for a school place,
OL,15,Fwith some waiting up to a year,
OL,16,Fespecially at secondary level,
OL,17,Faccording to the Refugee Council, with
OL,18,Fthese frequent, uncoordinated
OL,19,Faccommodation moves at short notice
OL,20,Fpartly to blame.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/20
