OL,6,F'We provide that stability for them':
OL,7,FRaj Mann, the Executive Head at the
OL,8,FCore Education Trust, told ITV News
OL,9,Fthat many of his students have at some
OL,10,Fpoint lived in Home Office hotels
OL,12,FSchools in England do receive money
OL,13,Ffrom local authorities for pupils who
OL,14,Fdon't speak English as a first
OL,15,Flanguage.
OL,17,FDepartment for Education figures show
OL,18,Fthat under the national funding
OL,19,Fformula for 2026/27, a total of #572
OL,20,Fmillion, which is 1.1% of the national
OL,21,Ffunding budget.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/20
