OL,6,FAt the Oasis Academy Aspinal, a
OL,7,Fprimary school in Manchester, they
OL,8,Fregularly receive an extra 25-30
OL,9,Fpupils throughout the year, but get no
OL,10,Fadditional budget to support them
OL,11,Fbecause of this rule.
OL,13,FAngela Sweeting, headteacher at Oasis
OL,14,FAcademy Aspinal, a primary school in
OL,15,FManchester, says technology has been a
OL,16,Fuseful tool to support children who
OL,17,Fspeak English as an additional language
