OL,3,CInside the Birmingham school
OL,4,Csupporting displaced children
OL,6,FHeadteacher Angela Sweeting told ITV
OL,7,FNews: "After the October census, we
OL,8,Fsupport families with things like
OL,9,Funiforms, food from our hub, their
OL,10,FiPads, so we're having to fund all of
OL,11,Fthat before we get the actual funding
OL,12,Fthe following academic year.
OL,14,F"So it would make a real difference if
OL,15,Fthe funding could be termly rather
OL,16,Fthan annually."
OL,18,FSweeting said every child gets a
OL,19,Fdevice until they leave in year six,
OL,20,Fwhich helps "translate the lessons
OL,21,Finto their home language."
