OL,6,FThe school is situated in an area with
OL,7,Fa large number of asylum seekers and
OL,8,Frefugees, with many families arriving
OL,9,Fwith little to no belongings, having
OL,10,Ffled war and persecution.
OL,12,FEducation leaders and unions said
OL,13,Finclusion across the sector for
OL,14,Fdisplaced children is "vital" and
OL,15,Fwithout significant change can often
OL,16,Fhave social, mental wellbeing and
OL,17,Flanguage-development repercussions.
