OL,6,FMatt Wrack, the General Secretary at
OL,7,FNASUWT, warned that the rights of
OL,8,Fdisplaced children were "often
OL,9,Foverlooked".
OL,11,F"Many asylum-seeking children face
OL,12,Fsignificant delays before being placed
OL,13,Fin a school after arrival or
OL,14,Frelocation to the country, which often
OL,15,Fhas a significantly detrimental impact
OL,16,Fon their education and ability to
OL,17,Fassimilate," he said.
