OL,6,FAt a time when the number of multi-
OL,7,Flingual students has steadily
OL,8,Fincreased over the last 25 year, Mr
OL,9,FWrack said the provision of support
OL,10,Fservices for children with EAL have
OL,11,Fbeen "subject to decades of decline",
OL,12,Fand the number of expert specialist
OL,13,Fteachers has "fallen sharply", making
OL,14,Fit "more challenging for schools".
OL,16,FWhile Mike Short, UNISON head of
OL,17,Feducation, told ITV News: "Given the
OL,18,Fpressure on mental health services,
OL,19,Fit's unlikely there's sufficient
OL,20,Fsupport available for traumatised
OL,21,Fchildren.
